'''Eidos Interactive''' is a [[Wikipedia:video game publisher|video game publisher]] that published ''[[LEGO Star Wars: The Video Game]]''. However, Eidos did not produce the sequel, ''[[LEGO Star Wars II: The Original Trilogy]]'', as [[LucasArts]] is the publisher.

Starting [[April 22]]nd, [[2009]], Eidos became a subsidiary of [[Wikipedia:Japan|Japanese]] video game developer and publisher [[Wikipedia:Square Enix|Square Enix]]

